&& python3 -m pip install --upgrade \
    pip \
    setuptools \
    setuptools_scm \
    wheel

ENV LANG=C.UTF-8

COPY . /girder/

# Build girder wheel file, and install it
RUN python3 setup.py bdist_wheel \
 && cd dist && python3 -m pip install girder && cd .. \
 && rm -rf build dist

RUN girder build

EXPOSE 8080

ENTRYPOINT ["girder", "serve"]
